Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate how it's come down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be able to fulfil my ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That money I gathered up \Nfrom those samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the powerless peasants \Nto take a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To help them take the step.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to make sure \NDororo understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What it is we're fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hidden the money \Npast the northern headland in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I might use it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for any great ambition, \Nbut for Dororo alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Engrave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to see it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will carry half of your ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other half...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛むのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:31.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,悔しいが…こうなっちゃもう、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:34.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の望みが叶うことはねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…侍どもから集めたあの金だけは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無駄にはできねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:52.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…力のねぇ農民たちが立ち上がって生きていくための、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大事な元手になるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:01.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいか。必ずどろろに連れてやってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちが…何のために戦い続けるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:08.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金の隠し場所は…北の岬を越えた先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:16.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたしは聞かないほうがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知ったらきっと使っちまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大願のためじゃなく、どろろ1人のためにね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここに入れておくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:45.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここなら自分じゃ見えないからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:50.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたの大願、半分はあたしがしょっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残りの半分は…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#14 The story of Sabame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So the map appears \Nwhenever your body is warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never taken a warm bath before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea I had that on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents have made you bear \Nquite a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit before my mama died...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen now, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your papa's lifelong ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry it on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the other half \Nwould always be close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd figure it out when I met someone \NI could truly trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get what she meant, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd more or less forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a wider range of choices now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you defeat all the demons \Nand get his body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Money's a grand thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a full belly, \Nyour heart will be calm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to see your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And start to think about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping true to your ambition  \N when it could mean life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't something just anyone can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you defeat a few demons \Nhere and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't change the world at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have on your back \Ncan move people and change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a source of great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, \Nyou have a lot more choices now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You could find the money \Nand live well on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or use it to build your own domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You could even go traveling \Nto some undiscovered land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take some time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to destroy Daigo's land \Nin exchange for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do \Nfrom here on out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, about what the priest said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After you defeat all the demons \Nand get your body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it wouldn't hurt to listen to me \Nonce in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, buy one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't leave me behind like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, buy one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone. What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num. Num-num!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you're crushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help me out, bro! \N-Carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a monster. Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry, carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're the one carrying me, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a hand, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num. Num-num!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, \NI'm the one that wants some num-num.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all burnt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least we'll be able \Nto stay dry during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pee-pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, I can't take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pee-pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, leave me out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pee-pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go pee-pee by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pee-pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it go pee outside in the bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there oil here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, somebody burnt this place down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Num-num. \N-You scared me to death, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hungry, too. \NWe don't have any food for monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't eat me! I don't taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Num-num...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I'd meet travelers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a curiosity you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not have known, \Nbut it's dangerous here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghoul haunts this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghoul...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my house if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't like to hear of people \Nbeing eaten in my mountain village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sabame. \NI am the lord of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear about your travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he isn't really a monster, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Lord Sabame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Out on watch? \NYou are such a hard working man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just looking out for my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in peace thanks to you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nwhere did that monster baby go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old country dance. \NDo you not like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,More please, lots of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a really great guy, \Nfeeding us strangers like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy listening to travelers' tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I've never left this land myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? But I bet you've got \Nsome interesting stories, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that ghoul in the burnt-out temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a pretty story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a nunnery up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The nun took in orphans  \N from the surrounding villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They were forced to work  \N like farm animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they disobeyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After working for a few years,  \N they'd be sold off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens must've had enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One night, lightning struck the temple  \N and set it alight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all gone in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nun, children, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful. All the kids, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We regretted not doing something earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for regrets, \Nbut we pray for those poor souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-And the ghoul? \N-It's the ghost of the nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't go up to heaven, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She appears nightly \Nand eats those that happen to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we weren't one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to stay here and rest \Nas long as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro? \NDo you believe everything he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About the ghoul, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And about how the temple \Nwas burnt down by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those oil stains must mean \Nsomebody set it on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a demon will come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not scared, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But jeez, this house sure is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have on your back  \N can move people and change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a source of great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen now, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your papa's lifelong ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?  \N I haven't the slightest clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping true to your ambition  \N when it could mean life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't something just anyone can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me.  \N I've been on my own all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to die, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, there's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, wake up! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro! \N-Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It spat silk? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It took the caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be some moth or butterfly monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This powder makes my skin tingle. \NIt's not poison, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use that pond in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey bro? Was that huge thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It took that caterpillar monster away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it came to save its kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Sabame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got you some food. \NTwo of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The children must be happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They could not eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You were beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The one The Twelfth could not devour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has come for what was taken from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let nothing and nobody \Nlay a finger on you or the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For my land and for my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほどねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体があったまると浮かび上がってくるって寸法かい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あったけぇ湯に入ったのなんて初めてだったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさかおいらの背中にそんなもんがあったなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほどねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんの親御も、えらいもんを背負わせたもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:25.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんが死ぬ…ちょっと前にさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかい、どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よーく覚えておき
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これはお父ちゃんの…命がけの願いなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が受け継いで、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,守っていくんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残りの半分は、おいらのすぐそばにいつもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:06.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらが心から信じられる相手に出会えたら、その時きっと分かるって…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほど？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んーまぁ、どういうことかさっぱりわかんなかったし、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,忘れたつもりでいたけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかったじゃないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これでお前さんたちの道が増えた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:27.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神どもを斬って身体を取り戻したとして、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その後はどうするね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金ってのはいいもんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹いっぱい食えれば、心も穏やかになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,周りを見る余裕が生まれて、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,明日のことを考え始める
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:56.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食うや食わずの身の上で、それでも志を貫けるのなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんの一握りだけだからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:07.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんたちが鬼神の何匹か斬ったところで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,世の中なんにも変わりゃしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんの背中のそれは、人を動かし世を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でかい力の源になる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、要は別のアテができたってことさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金を見つけて遊ぶもよし。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,新たな国を築くもよし。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:42.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰も知らない異国へ行くってのも悪かないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっ、坊さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここらでちょっくら考えるといいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、お前さんがどうしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:54.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,失くした身体と引き換えに醍醐の国を滅ぼしたいってんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,別だけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよそれ！あにきは別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なあ…あにき。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきはこの先…どうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神を討つ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくてさ！坊さんも言ってたろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神をみんな倒して身体全部取り戻したとして、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのあとの話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハァ…どうしたらいいと思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら…おいら…よくわかんねぇや。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:02.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ！？たまにはおいらの話ぐらい\N聞いてくれたってバチは当たんねぇだろ！？おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こうてくだされ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もー！ひでぇよあにき！置いてくなんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こうてくだされ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お頼み申します
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ、消えた？なんだよなんだよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！こいつら何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマ！マンマー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おんぶ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おんぶ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,重い！潰れる！うぅ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おんぶ…おんぶー…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助けて、あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けどバケモンだろ？助けてってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こらあにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おんぶ！おんぶー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これじゃおんぶじゃない！吊し上げだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…代わってくれよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:17.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマ…マンマー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったく…まんまが食いたいのはおいらの方だってぇの。ハァ…ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わぁ…あにき、寺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わー…中は黒焦げだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも夜露ぐらいは凌げるの…かな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おしっこ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:01.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じょ…冗談じゃねぇ！そこまで面倒見きれかるっての！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おしっこ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇ…やだ！おいら知らない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おしっこ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわぁ…！自分でしろってそのぐらい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おしっこー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わぁ～！やめろ！おい！離せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…何だい？それ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ、ちゃんと外の茂みにさせたから。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え、なに…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,油？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…なんでこんなところに油が？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここが燃えたのって、またか誰かが火を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマァー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマー\Nお前…心の臓が止まるかと思ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はそれどころじゃないんだってば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひぁっ！だいたいお前何食うんだってんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いらたちも腹ペコなのに、バケモン用のメシなんて！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…まさかお前のメシって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マーンー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ！喰わないで！おいら美味くないから！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マンマァー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助けて…あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ってぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんなところに旅の者とは。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奇特な人もあったものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた方は知るまいが、ここは夜は危ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしが出るのでな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:49.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よろしければ私の屋敷に来なさらんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:11.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わが里の内で人が喰い殺されるのをみすみす眺めても…おれぬのでな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はこの辺りの里を治める、鯖目と申す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:29.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたちの旅の話でも…聞かせてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:54.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁあにき。あいつ本当にバケモンじゃないんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど…臭う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お晩でがんす、鯖目様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夜回りですかい？相変わらずご精が出ますのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:21.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんの。己が里を己が手で守っておるだけのことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯖目様のおかげで、わしらも安泰ですじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういえばあいつ、どこ消えちまったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここが私の屋敷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁさ、遠慮なく通られい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,田舎芸でしてな。お気に召さぬかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかわり！てんこもりで！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんがと！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:29.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっさん、いいやつだな！\N見ず知らずのおいらたちにこんなにごちそうしてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,旅の者の話を聞くのが好きでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はこの地を離れたことがないゆえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか。でもここらにも面白そうな話ありそうだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっきの焼け跡のあやかしとかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気味のよい話ではないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこにはかつて尼寺があってな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:16.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,住職は近隣の里から身寄りのない子供を貰い受けておった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まるで牛か馬でも扱うように働かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞かねばたちまち…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:32.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうして何年かすると売り飛ばされてしまうのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天罰が下ったのだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ある夜、本堂に稲妻が落ちて火事となり…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっという間に焼け落ちてしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,住職も…子供達ももろともに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:58.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな…ひでぇじゃねぇかい。子供達までみんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:04.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々も、もう少し早く何とかしてやれなかったのかと…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:10.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今更だが、時折参って冥福を祈っておる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしは？\N住職の成れの果てだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:18.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,成仏できなかったのだろうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:22.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夜な夜な現れては、通りがかったものを喰らうのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかったー！おいらたち喰われなくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっさんのおかげだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは…何より
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、今日はもう遅い。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遠慮なくこの屋敷に逗留して休まれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:53.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ、あにき。さっきの話、どこまでホントだと思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,女の霊は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だよなぁ。それに雷落ちて寺が焼けたってのもさぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの油のシミはどう見ても着け火の跡だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いずれわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来ると思う？鬼神がここに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こ…怖いわけじゃねーからな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやー、なんか寒いなぁこの屋敷。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すきま風かなぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…寝ちゃった？ちぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:59.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さん背中のそれは、人を動かし世を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でかい力の源になる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかい、どろろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これはお父ちゃんの…命懸けの願いなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:15.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしろっていうんだよ…おいらわかんないよ）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:23.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食うや食わずの身の上で、それでも志を貫けるのなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:27.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんの一握りの人間だけだからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:33.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仕方ねーじゃねーかぃ。オイラずっと1人ぼっちだったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:45.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうして死んじゃったんだよ…おっかちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにき！なんか来てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！起きて起きて！あ…やばいってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！\N退がってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねば糸？おい、てめぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やったぁ！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な、なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわっ、なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？なんだこれ？ゲホッ！ゲホッ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、イモムシを！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひぇー、びっくりしたぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつきっと、蛾とか蝶のバケモンだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:06.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、この粉なんかピリピリするけど…得じゃないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,洗えるか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:13.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,庭の池、使っちまうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁあにき。あのでかいヤツって、やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつ、イモムシのバケモンを連れてったよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分の子供を助けに来たってことなのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:37.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯖目様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,久々の餌…それも2つもじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:48.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子らも、今日は満足したろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,喰えませ…なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…手強い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,討ち漏らしたというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12番目の喰い漏らし…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もや、取り戻しに来るとは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:08.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかな相手であろうとも、そなたらには指一本触れさせぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:14.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地と…この地に生きるわが民のために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love \Nthis accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world \Non our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maimai-onba"
